Howto
~~~~~
::

 import pds
 instance = pds.Pds()
 instance.session.Name
 .. 'kde'

 instance.session.Version
 .. '4'

 instance.home
 .. '/home/pars'

 instance.install_prefix
 .. '/usr/kde/4'

 instance.config_file
 .. '/home/pars/.kde4/share/config/kdeglobals'

 instance.config_path
 .. '/home/pars/.kde4/'

Test Scripts
~~~~~~~~~~~~

You can use following test scripts from $PYTHON_DIR/site-packages/pds/

 - test-pds.py (For GUI Test, requires PyQt)
 - test-cli.py (To get environment information)
 - test-qapp.py (For testing QUniqueApplication)

